---
title: get_data_column_sidecars (fulu-validator)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_assert : assert len(cells_and_kzg_proofs) == len(kzg_commitments)
    q_assert --> q_init_sidecars : sidecars = []
    q_init_sidecars --> q_col_iter : for column_index in range(NUMBER_OF_COLUMNS)
    q_col_iter --> q_init_cols : column_cells, column_proofs = [], []
    q_init_cols --> q_blob_iter : for cells, proofs in cells_and_kzg_proofs
    q_blob_iter --> q_append_cell : column_cells.append(cells[column_index])
    q_append_cell --> q_append_proof : column_proofs.append(proofs[column_index])
    q_append_proof --> q_blob_iter : next blob
    q_append_proof --> q_build : no more blobs
    q_build --> q_append_sidecar : sidecars.append(DataColumnSidecar(...))
    q_append_sidecar --> q_col_iter : next column
    q_append_sidecar --> [*] : no more columns, return sidecars

    note right of q_col_iter
        INV: len(cells_and_kzg_proofs) == len(kzg_commitments) (precondition)
        INV: Exactly NUMBER_OF_COLUMNS sidecars are produced
        INV: Each sidecar contains one cell and one proof per blob
        INV: DataColumnSidecar.index == column_index for each sidecar
    end note
